By Council Member Reed:
Pursuant to Rule 11.20b of the Council and Section 20-226(g) of the New York City Administrative Code, the Council resolves that the action of the Department of Transportation approving an unenclosed sidewalk cafe located at 364-366 West 110th Street, Spoonbread, Inc., d/b/a Spoonbread Too in Manhattan's Council District no 8 shall be subject to review by the Council.
